1806,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d3530264-Reviews-or1805-Novotel_London_Blackfriars-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Novotel London Blackfriars Hotel Reviews,Very modern and clean,"We stayed here overnight on 6th Oct. We arrived at 1.30pm (we were aware you can't usually check in until 2pm but we wanted to check in our bags) and the receptionist called housekeeping to check if our room was ready, which it was. So up we went to our 10th floor room, and immediately noticed an unmade bed, dirty glasses on the sides, wet towels hanging up in bathroom and rubbish in the bins! So back down to reception to tell them and to check in our bags and say we will return later. We returned around 3 hours later, and the reception staff were very apologetic for our earlier issue, but despite this, no complimentary drink or anything was offered. That would've been a nice touch considering. Anyway, after this were were extremely pleased with our room, very comfortable bed,…",Date of stay: October 2012,4.0
1807,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d3530264-Reviews-or1805-Novotel_London_Blackfriars-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Novotel London Blackfriars Hotel Reviews,Good location and brand new hotel,"It happened that I stayed here on the very first night of opening so not a typical stay.  There were lots of very helpful staff on hand and the room was clean (new!), the bed was very comfortable and all the general areas of the hotel were impressive.  This is a good location for South Bank, with easy access to city and main line stations.  Several bus routes run from right outside the hotel. Highly recommended and good value for money.",Date of stay: October 2012,4.0
